ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Armor Proficiency (Light)|TYPE:ACOLYTE.GENERAL.LAW_ENFORCEMENT.MILITARY.SOLDIER.DAREDEVIL.BODYGUARD.FIELDMEDIC.INVESTIGATOR.NEGOTIATOR.INFILTRATOR.DREADNOUGHT.FIELDOFFICER.HELIXWARRIOR.SPACEMONKEY.TECHNOSAVANT.TRACER.ARCANEARRANGER.MYSTIC.SHADOWHUNTER.STREETWARRIOR.TECHNOMAGE.SQUIRE|DESC:When a character wears a type of armor with which he or she is proficient, the character gets to add the armor's equipment bonus to his or her Defense. Also, the armor check penalty applies only to Balance, Climb, Escape Artist, Hide, Jump, Move Silently, and Tumble checks
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Double Tap|TYPE:GENERAL.INVESTIGATOR.FAST.GUNSLINGER.BODYGUARD.TRACER.MECHAJOCKEY.PSIONICAGENT|DESC:When using a semiautomatic firearm with at least two bullets loaded, the character may fire two bullets as a single attack against a single target. The character receives a -2 penalty on this attack, but deals +1 die of damage with a successful hit
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Stealthy|TYPE:TELEPATH.GENERAL.FAST.GUNSLINGER.INFILTRATOR.TRACER.WILDLORD.SHADOWKINDHUMAN|DESC:The character gets a +2 bonus on all Hide checks and Move Silently checks
